I'm working on a Julia interface for some C codes and I'm not sure what should I do for the structure :
```struct zqrm_spfct_type_c{
  int          *cperm_in;
  int           icntl[20];
  float         rcntl[10];
  long int      gstats[10];
  void         *h; 
};```
In Julia, it should be :
```mutable struct qrm_spfct{T} &lt;: Factorization{T}
  cperm_in :: Ptr{Cint}
  icntl    :: NTuple{20, Cint}
  rcntl    :: NTuple{10, Cfloat}
  gstats   :: NTuple{10, Clonglong}
  h        :: Ptr{Cvoid}```

